{
  "texts": [
    "On FF + +, with Deep-FakeTIMIT, the BFLDL achieves an accuracy of above 97%.",
    "Also, CelebDF has a detecting accuracy of 98.9%, whereas DFDCpre has a detecting accuracy of 98.1%.",
    "So the variations between various samples from different datasets are taken into account.",
    "Even when the compression rate is high, FF + + 's strong detection abilities on c40 samples are proved by its tolerable performance.",
    "When a variety of post-processing processes are applied, the good DFDC pre-performance demonstrates the detection capabilities."
  ]
}